%N A397256 Square array T(n,k) = product of digits of k >= 1 in base n >= 2, read by falling antidiagonals.
%F A397256 T(n, k) = T(n, n+k) = k for k < n [or n > k, column wise].
%F A397256 T(n, m*n + k) = m*k for 0 <= k < n, 0 < m < n.
